{"groups":[{"groupKey":"kakao:468897483159116","name":"kakao:468897483159116","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":1,"lastActive":1783482529968,"messages":[{"sender":"김소언","text":"{\"member\":{\"userId\":48718351,\"nickName\":\"김소언\"},\"kicked\":false,\"memorial\":false,\"hidden\":false,\"feedType\":2}","ts":1783482529968}]},{"groupKey":"120363429055836995@g.us","name":"120363429055836995@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":1,"lastActive":1783480640843,"messages":[{"sender":"Christoph Gebhard","text":"Hello everybody. We would like to take you up on your offer of a van to Incheon Airport. However, in addition to the one included in the price, we need a second van, as there are 9 of us plus our luggage. We would like to leave here at 6:00 a.m. on Friday so that we can arrive at the airport by 8:00 a.m.","ts":1783480640843}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:473131976143563","name":"kakao:473131976143563","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":13,"lastActive":1783479473334,"messages":[{"sender":"한수지","text":"카드 결제 링크 보내주실 수 있나요?","ts":1783475402149},{"sender":"한수지","text":"카드 결제 링크 보내주실 수 있나요?","ts":1783475403439},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"네네!","ts":1783475844703},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"네네!","ts":1783475845427},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"저희가 감사의 마음을 담아 추가 인원에 대한 비용은 면제 처리 해드리겠습니다 ^^","ts":1783476067292},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"저희가 감사의 마음을 담아 추가 인원에 대한 비용은 면제 처리 해드리겠습니다 ^^","ts":1783476067822},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"숙소 사용이 만족스러우셨다면 좋은 리뷰로 저희를 응원해주세요 ^^","ts":1783476080384},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"숙소 사용이 만족스러우셨다면 좋은 리뷰로 저희를 응원해주세요 ^^","ts":1783476081922},{"sender":"서윤","text":"너무너무 감사합니다 좋은 하루 되세요~~~!","ts":1783476879802},{"sender":"서윤","text":"너무너무 감사합니다 좋은 하루 되세요~~~!","ts":1783476880149},{"sender":"한수지","text":"감사합니다!!!☺️","ts":1783476964248},{"sender":"한수지","text":"감사합니다!!!☺️","ts":1783476964268},{"sender":".","text":"{\"member\":{\"userId\":22403042,\"nickName\":\".\"},\"kicked\":false,\"memorial\":false,\"hidden\":true,\"feedType\":2}","ts":1783479473334}]},{"groupKey":"120363422965145348@g.us","name":"120363422965145348@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":14,"lastActive":1783478270954,"messages":[{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"Hello. Flight AA281 is delayed. New expected landing time is 5:55pm. Thank you","ts":1783441710216},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Then, how many passengers are arriving on UA 893 and AA 281 respectively?","ts":1783444846382},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"UA 893 is 4 people\nAA281 is 3 people\n7 people total\n\n1 person switched to tomorrow","ts":1783445244877},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"First group is able tp wait for second group at airport.","ts":1783445316861},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"The waiting time will probably be too long\n\nSo We'll arrange one car for UA 893 (4 people) and one for AA 281 (3 people)\n\nHow about this?","ts":1783445490194},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"Great! Thank you! First car name for UA893 is for Jeffrey. \nI will be on the AA281","ts":1783445577642},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Ok noted.See you soon 😀","ts":1783445717886},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"Thank you!!!","ts":1783445735649},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"AA281 new arrival time 7:01","ts":1783452184597},{"sender":"Julia Halualani","text":"Sorry 8:01","ts":1783453294868},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Don't worry. The driver will track your flight and check your arrival time","ts":1783458284579},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello! 🇰🇷 @190061194801246 \n\nMy name is Cyrus Noh, and I’ll be your check-in host today.\n\nI’m here to help make your arrival smooth and comfortable, and to guide you through anything you may need for your check-in. 🏠✨\n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783477737405},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"when you go out to arrival hall, please find out your name board.","ts":1783477783793},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello 😊 I’ve invited today’s driver @66941494517817 to this group chat for easier coordination.","ts":1783478270954}]},{"groupKey":"120363427591564695@g.us","name":"COZE JT 8thJul Yan Ertek 4A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"JT","messageCount":4,"lastActive":1783478139947,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello! 🇰🇷 @61847696863341 \n\nMy name is Cyrus Noh, and I’ll be your check-in host today.\n\nI’m here to help make your arrival smooth and comfortable, and to guide you through anything you may need for your check-in. 🏠✨\n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783477394574},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"2:00 PM check-in is possible.\n\nCould you please let me know how you’ll be coming to the accommodation today, and where you’ll be departing from?\n\nWhen you leave your departure location, please send me a quick message with your estimated arrival time.\n\nI’ll be waiting near the accommodation entrance to welcome you and help with your check-in. 🏠✨","ts":1783477598514},{"sender":"Yan","text":"We will come around 1pm to seoul train station and take a taxi to home 👍🏼","ts":1783478006681},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Seoul Station pickup via I.M Taxi (van) 🚖\n\n👥 Capacity: up to 7 guests\n🧳 Luggage: up to 5 suitcases\n\nHow it works\n\n1. We don’t pre-assign a driver. Once you arrive at Seoul Station, please message us.\n\n\n2. If possible, let us know 3–4 minutes before you reach the pickup point.\n\n\n3. Our team will request an I.M Taxi van in real time and reply with the vehicle (plate) number and estimated pickup time.\n\n\n4. Meet the driver at the pickup point and confirm the plate number we send you.\n\n\n\nPlease keep your phone available for messages. If your timing changes, just give us a quick update—we’ll adjust right away. 💛\n\nCyrus, Guest Care Team of COZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783478139947}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:301321483004194","name":"kakao:301321483004194","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":8,"lastActive":1783478125613,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_Cyrus","text":"기사님 배정 부탁드립니다","ts":1783477821150},{"sender":"COZE_Cyrus","text":"기사님 배정 부탁드립니다","ts":1783477821383},{"sender":"변이규","text":"변이규90","ts":1783477858096},{"sender":"변이규","text":"변이규90","ts":1783477858846},{"sender":"변이규","text":"젆형복110","ts":1783478117825},{"sender":"변이규","text":"젆형복110","ts":1783478118643},{"sender":"변이규","text":"전형복\n핸드폰 010 4766 7889","ts":1783478124223},{"sender":"변이규","text":"전형복\n핸드폰 010 4766 7889","ts":1783478125613}]},{"groupKey":"120363407384623871@g.us","name":"120363407384623871@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":2,"lastActive":1783477288199,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello! 🇰🇷 @188584162275518 \nYour check-in host today will be Ricky from our Guest Care Team.\n\nHe will help make your arrival smooth and comfortable, and guide you through anything you may need for your check-in. 🏠✨\n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783477265811},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"when you go out to arrival hall, please find out your name board.","ts":1783477288199}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:473051438439374","name":"kakao:473051438439374","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":2,"lastActive":1783476181913,"messages":[{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"숙소 사용이 만족스러우셨다면, 좋은 리뷰로 저희를 응원해주세요 ^^","ts":1783476181075},{"sender":"GAYA | GUEST CARE","text":"숙소 사용이 만족스러우셨다면, 좋은 리뷰로 저희를 응원해주세요 ^^","ts":1783476181913}]},{"groupKey":"120363426846640888@g.us","name":"120363426846640888@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":1,"lastActive":1783475912325,"messages":[{"sender":"Ricky, Tour Host","text":"/exp jy 400000 tour","ts":1783475912325}]},{"groupKey":"wechat:26313916487@chatroom","name":"wechat:26313916487@chatroom","platform":"WeChat","messageCount":2,"lastActive":1783474950194,"messages":[{"sender":"wxid_i9piwpit0n7i12","text":"你好 住在你们这里真的很舒适很赞，现在已经回国啦～想问下你们用的洗发水是什么牌子？很好用，想自己买一瓶，方便的话可以告知一下麻，谢谢！","ts":1783474626873},{"sender":"wxid_i9piwpit0n7i12","text":"谢谢～","ts":1783474950194}]},{"groupKey":"wechat:26863426701@chatroom","name":"wechat:26863426701@chatroom","platform":"WeChat","messageCount":3,"lastActive":1783473440663,"messages":[{"sender":"wxid_1610706276821","text":"行李可以具体寄存哪里","ts":1783472576032},{"sender":"COZE_Cyrus","text":"2580*","ts":1783473237443},{"sender":"COZE_Cyrus","text":"Hello! Your luggage has been safely stored on the 1st floor.\n\nIf you arrive before 3:00 PM, you may enter the 1st floor with the password 2580 and take your luggage first.\n\n\nThank you! 🙏","ts":1783473440663}]},{"groupKey":"120363428539886519@g.us","name":"COZE JTS 8thJul Diana Li 1A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"JTS","messageCount":20,"lastActive":1783470726833,"messages":[{"sender":"D","text":"Hi there! My plane landed much earlier than","ts":1783455823955},{"sender":"D","text":"Just wanted to confirm if earlier check in is possible?","ts":1783455877864},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Yes! Your accommodation is fully ready for check-in, so you can check in now.\n\nPlease refer to the manual provided above. We wish you a safe journey to the property.","ts":1783457852776},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Yes! Your accommodation is fully ready for check-in, so you can check in now","ts":1783457886756},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Here we share the brief info of home and neighborhood!","ts":1783457947558},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Home address :","ts":1783457948115},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"서울특별시 종로구 낙산3길 27-1","ts":1783457948654},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Main Gate Key Box Pin 3 3 8 8","ts":1783457949214},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"(Please keep the key in the keybox. that key is shared)","ts":1783457990407},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Front Door Pin 260708 *","ts":1783458030604},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"House Manual","ts":1783458085578},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"The neighborhood information.\nyou can find all of info about our neighborhood  here!\nhttps://naver.me/5EaMQnFs","ts":1783458129178},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"🏠 COZE JTS Tailored Service Residence – Guest Manual\n\n👋 Welcome to COZE Hospitality 3.0!\nWe’re delighted to have you here in Daehakro(University Street)! To help you settle in comfortably, we’ve prepared this quick guide.\n\nHave a wonderful stay with COZE! 🏡✨\n\n📌 Essential Information\n\nAddress — \n\n서울특별시 종로구 낙산3길 27-1\n\n27-1, Naksan 3-gil, Jongno-gu, Seoul, Republic of Korea\n03088\n\nMain Gate Key Box Pin 3 3 8 8\n(please keep the key inside after use)\n\nYour Suite Door Code \n\n— Check‑in date in the format YYMMDD + *\n\nExample: 10 May 2025 → 250510* (remains the same throughout your stay)\n\nWi‑Fi Networks\n\nSSID  TEVA_STUDIO\nPIN  teva3388#*\n\n📱 Guest Smartphone Provided\n\nA smartphone with a Korean phone number and unlimited data & calls is provided free of charge during your stay!\nAll essential apps are pre-installed, and the phone can be used as a portable Wi-Fi hotspot.\n\nUse it to:\n🍽️ Order food\n🚕 Call taxis\n🌐 Browse the internet\n🗺️ Navigate the neighborhood\n\n💡 Local Tip:\nOpen the Naver Map app — we’ve bookmarked a detailed local guide with:\n🍜 Hidden gem restaurants\n🏪 Supermarkets & convenience stores\n🏥 Hospitals & clinics\n💳 ATMs & banks\n\nIt’s like having a local guide in your pocket 📍😉\n\n💡 Local Tip:\nCheck out the Naver Map app — we’ve bookmarked great local spots like restaurants, supermarkets, banks, clinics, and more. It’s like having a local guide in your pocket! 🗺📍\n\n🍽 Food Delivery Orders\nUse the guest smartphone to open the Coupang Eats app.\nAdd your items to the cart, take a screenshot of the final summary, and send it to us via Messenger.\nWe’ll place the order and pay for it. You can reimburse us in cash or cryptocurrency at checkout.\n\n🚖 MPV Taxi Booking\nWe can assist you with real-time bookings via IM TAXI.\nMPV taxis seat up to 7 people — ideal for groups. Fares are approx. 30% higher than standard taxis.\nNeed multiple vans? No problem — just expect a short delay.\n\n☕ Capsule Coffee & Tea\nExtra tea and coffee capsules are in the drawer beneath the living room tea cabinet. Feel free to help yourself!\n\nilly Coffee Machine\n\nQuick Guide\nhttps://youtu.be/XEDAXZY50FM?si=uOfwquZXC6WCis_G\n\nSteam Milk\nhttps://youtu.be/bTzG7iM4dMA?si=aiEWUseiOT0as-Jo\n\nProgram the Volume\nhttps://youtu.be/h2X5gLYpf_4?si=eaDtARcyGQTjddFz\n\n♻️ Food Waste Disposal\nA garbage disposal is built into the sink.\nTurn on the water, press the foot pedal, and it will grind away food waste.\n\n⚠️ No bones or shells, please!\n\n🗑️ Trash & Recycling\n\nInside of Main gate, You can find the big two trash bin. One is for general waste, The other is for \n\nIf it’s full, let us know — we’ll take care of it. Ask us about Korean waste rules anytime!\n\n🖥️ Office Desk Setup\nInstead of a TV, we’ve prepared a home office setup for your convenience. A 27-inch monitor and mini PC are connected to an all-in-one printer with unlimited ink — perfect for work or casual use.\n\n🧴 Supplies, Towels & Amenities\nExtra supplies, including tissues, body/face/foot towels, and a box of amenities are stored in the overhead cabinet above the bed. Please help yourself to anything you need!\n\n💬 Inquiries & Assistance\nNeed help or have any questions?\nJust message us anytime via Messenger!\nOur team will reply promptly to support you.\n\nWe're just one tap away — happy to help!\n\nEnjoy your stay with COZE and make yourself at home!","ts":1783458129740},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Yes, your room is all set, so you can check in now! \n\nPlease check the guide above, and hope you have a safe trip here.","ts":1783458174904},{"sender":"D","text":"Thank you so much :)","ts":1783459857633},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello! 🇰🇷 @86367581282366 \nMy name is Cyrus Noh, and I’ll be your check-in host for today.\n\nThe important self check-in details, including the password, are pinned at the top of this chat. Please check the pinned message when you arrive. 🏠✨\n\nAfter using the gate key, please return it to the key box right away. 🔑\n\nIf you have any questions or need anything, please feel free to let us know anytime.\n\nI’ll be around the accommodation area between 12:00 PM and 2:00 PM today, so if the timing works, I’d be happy to stop by briefly and say hello. 😊\n\nCOZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1783470313958},{"sender":"D","text":"Hi Cyrus! Thank you so much, I have just arrived and already got in 👍🏻I would love to say hi but I have to leave for my appointment in a bit, hopefully I’d be able to say hello some other time 😊","ts":1783470459630},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Thank you so much for letting us know! 😊\nI’m glad to hear you arrived and checked in smoothly.\n\nNo worries at all — please enjoy your appointment.","ts":1783470544026},{"sender":"D","text":"Thank you for your hospitality 😊","ts":1783470567370},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Just a quick note about the shower 🚿\n\nThe shower head is installed on the ceiling, above the sink area.\nPlease use the faucet control near the sink, and switch the water direction using the small knob/lever on the faucet.\n\nOnce you switch it, the water will come down from the ceiling shower head. 😊\n\nIf you have any trouble, please let us know anytime.","ts":1783470726833}]},{"groupKey":"120363410279865987@g.us","name":"COZE SJ 13thAug Wesley Brown 4A2K","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"SJ","messageCount":1,"lastActive":1783469289608,"messages":[{"sender":"COZE_Gaya","text":"@151432628060212  Hello :)","ts":1783469289608}]},{"groupKey":"120363423605030782@g.us","name":"120363423605030782@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":2,"lastActive":1783467438166,"messages":[{"sender":"Anh","text":"Hi Gaya, just got the flight details. \nFlight number TG656\nJuly 13 06:55 terminal 1","ts":1783467268757},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Hello @127290012922015 \n\nWe have confirmed your flight information. We will arrange two vans for your arrival. \n\nWe look forward to seeing you on July 13th!","ts":1783467438166}]},{"groupKey":"120363427651504347@g.us","name":"COZE BS 20thDec Sophia Hwang 8A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"BS","messageCount":1,"lastActive":1783451831340,"messages":[{"sender":"Sophia HWANG","text":"Thank you, Gaya.  Your information about future home plans gives me something to look forward to.  Even to people who canceled the reservation, you are showing the integrity of your service.  That is impressive.  Thank you & keep up the good work.  I'd like to keep your contact information or your email (if available) for future reference & I will recommend COZE to my friends for sure.","ts":1783451831340}]},{"groupKey":"120363411036797238@g.us","name":"COZE HT 15thSept Arianne Panganiban 8A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"HT","messageCount":3,"lastActive":1783435461976,"messages":[{"sender":"Arianne Panganiban","text":"Hi 😊","ts":1783434912320},{"sender":"Arianne Panganiban","text":"Thank you so much 😊","ts":1783435440307},{"sender":"Arianne Panganiban","text":"Cebu pacific  \nManila to seoul:\n sept 15 7:35pm - 12:45 am (incheon airport terminal 1)\n\nSeoul to manila\nSept 21 6:35 am - 9:55am (incheon ariport terminal 1)\n\nFlight details\n\nWill be total of 8 guest 😊","ts":1783435461976}]}]}